      <scopecontent id="aspace_120e84224d88577cd4dd2ff5b701be9b">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of audiotapes and videotapes documenting Eugene Shoemaker's 1996 lecture "Near Earth Asteroids and Comets" and James Anderson's 2002 lecture, and photographs and videorecordings documenting the Tercentenary Silliman Memorial Symposium, "A Remembrance of Times Past: The Development of Earth and Its Life."</p>  
      </scopecontent>
